The paper deals with natural language processing and deep learning techniques to generate SQL queries from natural language questions on multi-relational healthcare data. This falls under the intersection of computer science and healthcare, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it deals with natural language processing. cs.DB (Databases) is also a likely category as the paper deals with relational databases. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also possible categories as the paper uses deep learning techniques. Finally, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with retrieving information from healthcare data.
